Hey Mike,
factory OEM manifolds, SP and DP and end pieces are available through many of
the advertisers in the VW mags. In fact, you can buy manifolds for just about
any configuration desired. I buy new DP center sections and end pieces
regularly, I just look for who has the best prices that month. CB Performance
and several others also sell performance end castings that "they say" give you
better flow.

67 Single Cab, DP 1641cc 34 PICT-3
